title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 13 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 13 2022
description:
Sen. Josh Hawley covers it all with Clay and Buck: No Dem shenanigans off limits. Biden openly demands censorship from Big Tech. Buck says, "They don't even pretend to care about free speech and the First Amendment anymore." Big win for liberty! SCOTUS blocks Biden's business vaccine mandate. Clay explains Biden's OSHA mandate "does not apply" if you work for an employer with 100 or more employees, as two-thirds of us do. C&B take calls.
